c: 72
v: 18
t: "wan almasajid lebadt allah whdh, fala taebuduu fiha ghyrh, wa'akhlasuu lah alduea' walebadt fyha; fa'iina almasajid lm tubn 'iilaa lyuebad allh wahdah fyha, dun min swah, wafi hdha wjwb tnzyh almasajid min kl ma yshwb al'iikhlas llh, wamutabaeat rasulih muhamad salaa allah ealayh wslm"